data.description: Discover style and comfort in this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms home nestled in the coveted Northampton neighborhood. As you step into the front living room, the open area is perfect for entertaining as it connects to a large eating space. The charming fireplace helps create a perfect setting. The heart of the home lies in the updated kitchen where modern conveniences are found. A large sunroom/den provides an expansive space of natural light offering a view of the backyard, which is perfect for outdoor enjoyment. The attached garage provides convenience and storage for its new owners. Schedule your private showing today!
